<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qchart-qtcharts.xml">QChart</db:link> class provides two methods that map between the scene coordinates and the series domain (defined by the axes ranges).</db:para>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qpointf.xml">QPointF</db:link> <db:link xlink:href="qchart-qtcharts.xml#mapToPosition">QChart::mapToPosition</db:link>(const <db:link xlink:href="qpointf.xml">QPointF</db:link> &amp;value, <db:link xlink:href="qabstractseries-qtcharts.xml">QAbstractSeries</db:link> *series)</db:para>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qpointf.xml">QPointF</db:link> <db:link xlink:href="qchart-qtcharts.xml#mapToValue">QChart::mapToValue</db:link>(const <db:link xlink:href="qpointf.xml">QPointF</db:link> &amp;position, <db:link xlink:href="qabstractseries-qtcharts.xml">QAbstractSeries</db:link> *series)</db:para>
